description:
SctpEndpoint: Table containing operational parameters of SCTP endpoints in a 5G NR network.

dateTime: Timestamp of data record.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier.
Id3:  Identifier for the type of SCTP endpoint.
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format.
SctpEndpoint.userLabel: User-defined label.
SctpEndpoint.dtlsSctpSecurityMode:  DTLS/SCTP security mode (e.g., DISABLED).
SctpEndpoint.dtlsNodeCredential: DTLS node credentials.
SctpEndpoint.reservedBy:  Resource reservation information.
SctpEndpoint.operationalState: Operational status (e.g., ENABLED).
SctpEndpoint.availabilityStatus: Availability status.
SctpEndpoint.localIpAddress: Local IP address and associated network information.
SctpEndpoint.dtlsTrustCategory: DTLS trust category.
SctpEndpoint.sctpProfile: SCTP profile information.
SctpEndpoint.sctpEndpointId: Unique identifier of the SCTP endpoint.
SctpEndpoint.portNumber: Port number used by the SCTP endpoint.
